The bug is a classic off-by-one error on **line 7** of `src/utils.ts`. The loop condition excludes the last array element by using `items.length - 1` instead of `items.length`. The fix is simple: remove the `- 1` from the loop condition. The test suite clearly shows what the expected behavior should be, and the first test case will expose this bug immediately when run.

